{"word":"H3282 - יַעַן - yaʻan - yah'-an - Because","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">יַעַן</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>yaʻan"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>yah'-an"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Because"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"நிமித்தம், படியினால், படியால், படி, ஆகையால்ஆனாலும், ஆதலால் - எச்சம்"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"because, therefore, be cause that, on account of"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> From an unused root meaning to <i>pay attention</i>; properly <i>heed</i>; by implication <i>purpose</i> (sake or account); used adverbially to indicate the <i>reason</i> or cause: - because (that), forasmuch (+ as), seeing then, + that, + whereas, + why."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H3282 - יַעַן - yaʻan - yah'-an/3282\">H3282</a>, <a href=\"#/H4616 - מַעַן - maʻan - mah'-an/4616\">H4616</a>, <a href=\"#/H4617 - מַעֲנֶה - maʻăneh - mah-an-eh'/4617\">H4617</a>, <a href=\"#/H5772 - עֹונָה - ʻôwnâh - o-naw'/5772\">H5772</a>, <a href=\"#/H6030 - עָנָה - ʻânâh - aw-naw'/6030\">H6030</a>, <a href=\"#/H6256 - עֵת - ʻêth - ayth/6256\">H6256</a>, <a href=\"#/H6258 - עַתָּה - ʻattâh - at-taw'/6258\">H6258</a>, <a href=\"#/H6261 - עִתִּי - ʻittîy - it-tee'/6261\">H6261</a>, <a href=\"#/H6262 - עַתַּי - ʻAttay - at-tah'ee/6262\">H6262</a>, <a href=\"#/H6278 - עֵת קָצִין - ʻÊth Qâtsîyn - ayth kaw-tseen'/6278\">H6278</a>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"}]}